<h1 id="3二分查找">3.二分查找</h1>
<h2 id="整数二分的基本流程">整数二分的基本流程</h2>

<div style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8;">
   <h2 id="二分查找法步骤">二分查找法步骤</h2>
<p>1.确定目标所满足的性质，是求左边界还是右边界（<code>&gt;=</code> 还是 <code>&lt;=</code>）</p>
<p>2.确定 <code>mid</code> 的计算方法：</p>
<ul>
<li>A. 对于左边界问题，$mid = \frac{l + r}{2} $</li>
<li>B. 对于右边界问题，$mid = \frac{l + r + 1}{2} $</li>
</ul>
<p>3.更新目标区间范围：</p>
<ul>
<li>A. 对于左边界问题，如果 <code>check(mid) = true</code>，则使 <code>r = mid</code>；如果 <code>check(mid) = false</code>，则使 <code>l = mid + 1</code></li>
<li>B. 对于右边界问题，如果 <code>check(mid) = true</code>，则使 <code>l = mid</code>；如果 <code>check(mid) = false</code>，则使 <code>r = mid - 1</code></li>
</ul>
<p>该问题通过多次迭代，缩小目标所在的区间范围（初始区间范围为 $[l, r]$）。</p>

</div>


<h2 id="整数二分的代码模板">整数二分的代码模板</h2>

<div style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8;">
   模板中的check(mid)函数需要根据查找问题的不同自行设计。
</div>


<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-C++" data-lang="C++"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#00688b;font-weight:bold">int</span> <span style="color:#008b45">bsearch_1</span>(<span style="color:#00688b;font-weight:bold">int</span> l,<span style="color:#00688b;font-weight:bold">int</span> r) <span style="color:#228b22">//左边界问题
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#228b22"></span>{  
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>	<span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">while</span>(l&lt;r)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>	{
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>     <span style="color:#00688b;font-weight:bold">int</span> mid=l+r&gt;&gt;<span style="color:#b452cd">1</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>	 <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span>(check(mid))	r=mid;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>	 <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">else</span>	l=mid+<span style="color:#b452cd">1</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>	}
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>	<span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> l;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>}
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#00688b;font-weight:bold">int</span> <span style="color:#008b45">bsearch_2</span>(<span style="color:#00688b;font-weight:bold">int</span> l,<span style="color:#00688b;font-weight:bold">int</span> r)<span style="color:#228b22">//右边界问题
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#228b22"></span>{  
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>	<span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">while</span>(l&lt;r)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>	{
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>     <span style="color:#00688b;font-weight:bold">int</span> mid=l+r+<span style="color:#b452cd">1</span>&gt;&gt;<span style="color:#b452cd">1</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>	 <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span>(check(mid))	l=mid;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>	 <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">else</span>	r=mid-<span style="color:#b452cd">1</span>;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>	}
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>	<span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> l;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>}
</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id="浮点数二分">浮点数二分</h2>

<div style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8;">
   浮点数二分不需要考虑边界问题，因此只需要在第一套模板的基础上，修改while条件为r-l&gt;某一个极小精度值，即满足r-l趋于0时，才循环停止。
</div>


